				"description": "<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-98d7599c-7fff-8b4f-ffa6-9733f686ea96\"><strong>Searing:</strong> On hit, target ignites, taking 1d6 persistent fire damage on the start of its next turn. Particularly flammable targets may continue to burn.</span></p>"
